text: Lilian Janse-van der Weele (born 1973 in Flushing) is a Dutch politician. She has been a member of the municipal council of Flushing (Vlissingen in Dutch) since 2014, and also the first female politician of the Reformed Political Party (SGP). == References == * Vlissingen Website Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch Calvinists Category:Dutch councillors Category:People from Vlissingen Category:Politicians from Zeeland Category:Reformed Political Party politicians
